1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Title: "Echoes of War"

Scene: A battlefield, sunrise.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:04,250
A soldier stands amid ruins, holding a tattered flag.

3
00:00:04,250 --> 00:00:05,000
Distant explosions echo.

4
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,750
He looks down at a photo of his family, then up, determined, towards the horizon.

5
00:00:08,750 --> 00:00:12,000
Voiceover: "In the face of chaos, humanity's spirit burns brightest."

Fade to black.

6
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:13,750
Text: "Remember the past, build the future."